nodes.text: Veneb Drassk was a male Trandoshan who used the Wookiee Gwarror to eliminate his rivals and ascend to a position of power and acquire a clan. He nearly became the Clan Speaker for all Trandoshan clans, but was killed on Taris around 3641 BBY by Qyzen Fess and the Barsen'thor of the Jedi Order.
